      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it's in such incredible shape it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014pristine interior, flawless paint, and it drives like a dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect ride that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
