    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in exemplary condition. This unit features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine, boasting a high-compression ratio and six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanical integrity is paramount; this example has undergone a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension kinematics remain sharp, and the engine's 8,000 RPM redline is reached with surgical precision. This is a zero-fault, analog driver\u2019s car with flawless paint depth and a pristine undercarriage.",
