    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece for the discerning buyer: a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as though it just departed the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, having been preserved under a ceramic coating and stored in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of untouched luxury; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple without a single crease or sign of wear, and the original protective films are still present on several door sills. Every mechanical component has been maintained with obsessive precision, backed by a comprehensive folder of service records from authorized specialists. The engine bay is concours-level clean, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or weathering. This is not merely a used car; it is a time capsule. From the crisp tactile feedback of every switch to the flawless alloy wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber, no detail has been overlooked. This vehicle has never seen rain, has never been smoked in, and carries a clean title with zero accidents.",
      "price": 48500.0,
