    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014always garaged, never a scratch, and the interior still has that fresh smell! It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
